---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy — BBQ It Guide" description="Privacy policy for the BBQ It Guide fan site. Covers data collection, advertising, cookies, and children's privacy.">
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: June 2026</p>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">About This Site</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">This website is an unofficial fan-made guide for the Roblox game BBQ It. We are not affiliated with, endorsed by, or connected to Roblox Corporation or the BBQ It development team.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Information We Collect</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">We do not require user accounts or collect personal information directly. However, the following third-party services may collect data when you use our site:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        <li><strong>Google Analytics (GA4):</strong> We use GA4 to understand site traffic, popular pages, and user behavior. This includes anonymized data about your browser, device, and visit patterns.</li>
        <li><strong>Cloudflare Web Analytics:</strong> We use Cloudflare Analytics for performance and traffic monitoring.</li>
        <li><strong>Adsterra:</strong> Our advertising partner may use cookies and tracking technologies to serve relevant ads. Third-party personalized ads may be displayed based on your browsing behavior.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Local Storage</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">Our calculator tools may save your last-used inputs in your browser's local storage for convenience. This data never leaves your device and is not transmitted to any server.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">This site covers content related to a Roblox game, which may attract younger audiences. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you are a parent or guardian and believe your child has interacted with our site in a way that concerns you, please <a href="/contact/" class="text-orange-500 underline">contact us</a>.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Third-Party Advertising</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">Third-party ad networks, including Adsterra, may use cookies, web beacons, and similar technologies to collect information about your visits to this and other websites. This information is used to provide advertisements about goods and services that may be of interest to you. You can opt out of personalized advertising through network-level controls or browser settings.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Cookies</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">This site uses cookies for analytics and advertising purposes. You can disable cookies in your browser settings, but some site features may not function properly.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">If you have questions about this privacy policy, please visit our <a href="/contact/" class="text-orange-500 underline">Contact page</a>.</p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
